com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.servers.serverhardware

Class ServerHardware

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.BaseModelResource
      • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.servers.serverhardware.ServerHardware
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ServerHardware
extends BaseModelResource
    The ServerHardware data transfer object (DTO) contains the information used to represent a server hardware in the system. It is passed in to the add/update server hardware REST api, as well as the add/update server hardware through java client api.
